quran[18{c,v,t}:
71,11,woh tum par aasman se khoob barishain barsaye ga
71,12,"tumhe maal aur aulaad se nawaze ga, tumahray liye baagh peda kere ga aur tumahray liye nhrin jari kar day ga"
71,13,tumhe kya ho gaya hai ke Allah ke liye tum kisi Waqar ki tawaqqa nahi rakhtay ?
71,14,halaank uss ne terhan terhan se tumhe banaya hai
71,15,kya dekhte nahi ho ke Allah ne kis terhan saat aasman teh Bar teh banaye
71,16,aur unn mein chaand ko noor aur Sooraj ko chairag banaya ?
71,17,aur Allah ne tum ko zameen se ajeeb terhan ugaya
71,18,phir woh tumhe aِsi zameen mein wapas le jaye ga aur iss se yakayak tum ko nikaal khara kere ga
71,19,aur Allah ne zameen ko tumahray liye farsh ki terhan bichaa diya
71,20,"taakay tum is ke andar khulay raastoon mein chalo """
71,21,"Nooh ne kaha,"" mere rab, onhon ne meri baat radd kar di aur unn ( raeesaon ) ki pairwi ki jo maal aur aulaad pa kar aur ziyada namuraad ho gay hain"
71,22,inn logon ne bara bhaari makr ka jaal phela rakha hai
71,23,"unhon ne kaha hargiz nah chhorro apne mabodon ko, aur nah chhorro With aur sawa ko, aur nah yaghus aur yaook aur nasar ko"
71,24,"unhon ne bohat logon ko gumraah kya hai, aur to bhi inn zaalmon ko gumraahi ke siwa kisi cheez mein taraqqi nah day """
71,25,"apni khataon ki bana par hi woh ghark kiye gay aur aag mein jhonk diye gay, phir unhon ne apne liye Allah se bachanay wala koi madadgaar nah paaya"
71,26,"aur Nooh ne kaha,"" mere rab, inn kafiroon mein se koi zameen par basnay wala nah chore"
71,27,agar to ne inn ko chore diya to yeh tairay bundon ko gumraah karen ge aur inn ki nasal se jo bhi peda hoga badkaar aur sakht kafir hi hoga
71,28,"mere rab, mujhe aur mere walidain ko aur har is shakhs ko jo mere ghar mein momin ki hesiyat se daakhil howa hai, aur sab momin mardon aur aurton ko maaf farma day, aur zaalmon ke liye halakat ke siwa kisi cheez mein izafah nah kar """
